|\ISS                                                           https://k1ss.org
________________________________________________________________________________


KISS repository with linked packages and submodules.
________________________________________________________________________________

Solution to: https://github.com/kisslinux/repo/issues/209


Example setup
________________________________________________________________________________

$ git submodule add https://github.com/kisslinux/repo

# Symlink everything
$ cd dylan-repo/zlib
$ ln -s ../../repo/core/zlib/<file> <file>


# If one cares about dirtying the repository.
# ie, if you're using a KISS repo in a push/pull manner.
# (Tell git to ignore changes to submodule.)
$ git config submodule.<name>.ignore all


